(2063, 1, '2017-12-07 15:45:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\n    "sage-theme-psm/resources::home_page_presentation_section_title": {\n        "value": "PASSIONN\\u00c9S ET SUPER MOTIV\\u00c9S !s",\n        "type": "theme_mod",\n        "user_id": 1,\n        "date_modified_gmt": "2017-12-07 14:45:38"\n    },\n    "sage-theme-psm/resources::home_page_presentation_section_text": {\n        "value": "<p>Chez PSM, votre <b>passion</b> sera la cl\\u00e9 de votre r\\u00e9ussite. Que vous ayez un profil de graphiste, communicant, d\\u00e9veloppeur, informaticien, ou que vous soyez tout simplement <b>motiv\\u00e9</b> et passionn\\u00e9 par <b>l\\u2019innovation</b>, le multim\\u00e9dia et les nouvelles technologies, nous allons vous transmettre les <b>outils</b> et les <b>exp\\u00e9riences</b> n\\u00e9cessaires \\u00e0 faire de vous un professionnel qualifi\\u00e9 dans votre domaine de pr\\u00e9dilection. Vous visez <b>l\\u2019excellence</b> pour la poursuite de vos \\u00e9tudes en <b>BAC+3</b> ou en <b>Master</b> ? PSM pourrait \\u00eatre la r\\u00e9ponse : venez d\\u00e9couvrir nos <a href=\\"#\\">formations</a> et nos <a>modalit\\u00e9s d\\u2019admission</a>.s</p>",\n        "type": "theme_mod",\n        "user_id": 1,\n        "date_modified_gmt": "2017-12-07 14:45:38"\n    },\n    "sage-theme-psm/resources::home_page_presentation_section_admission_link": {\n        "value": "http://tetsts",\n        "type": "theme_mod",\n        "user_id": 1,\n        "date_modified_gmt": "2017-12-07 14:45:38"\n    }\n}', '', '', 'auto-draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8c8108b9-a9e5-4cfc-804f-61599358806b', '', '', '2017-12-07 15:45:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/site-psm-back/?p=2063', 0, 'customize_changeset', '', 0),
(2064, 1, '2017-12-07 15:47:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\n    "sage-theme-psm/resources::home_page_presentation_section_admission_link": {\n        "value": "http://tetsts",\n        "type": "theme_mod",\n        "user_id": 1,\n        "date_modified_gmt": "2017-12-07 14:47:01"\n    },\n    "sage-theme-psm/resources::home_page_projects_section_title": {\n        "value": "Des formations orient\\u00e9es projetss",\n        "type": "theme_mod",\n        "user_id": 1,\n        "date_modified_gmt": "2017-12-07 14:47:01"\n    },\n    "sage-theme-psm/resources::home_page_projects_section_text": {\n        "value": "<p>Les <b>projets multim\\u00e9dia</b> sont le pain quotidien des \\u00e9tudiants de PSM. Chaque ann\\u00e9e, ils sont amen\\u00e9s \\u00e0 r\\u00e9aliser un vrai projet d\\u2019<b>\\u00e9quipe</b>, en totale autonomie et dans des <b>conditions r\\u00e9elles</b> (et cela, en plus des projets sp\\u00e9cifiques aux unit\\u00e9s d\\u2019enseignements).<br /> Ces <b>exp\\u00e9riences concr\\u00e8tes</b>, en plus d\\u2019\\u00eatre extr\\u00eamement formatrices et valorisantes, aboutissent souvent \\u00e0 des r\\u00e9sultats remarquables.<br /> D\\u00e9couvrez les projets r\\u00e9alis\\u00e9s au fil des ann\\u00e9es par nos \\u00e9tudiant dans la section d\\u00e9di\\u00e9e de ce site !ss</p>",\n        "type": "theme_mod",\n        "user_id": 1,\n        "date_modified_gmt": "2017-12-07 14:47:01"\n    }\n}', '', '', 'auto-draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '64b530f9-04fc-4da6-a9c5-3fc0c1a73b4d', '', '', '2017-12-07 15:47:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/site-psm-back/?p=2064', 0, 'customize_changeset', '', 0),
